{"about_the_game":"<strong>Brilliant Jigsaw is a puzzle-based game full of joy and freedom, where you'll unlock various &quot;super&quot; abilities and quickly immerse yourself in the fun of puzzle-solving. </strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/Puzzle_Pieces_Falling_03.gif?t=1735785209\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lighthearted and joyful. </h2><br>The game combines traditional puzzle-solving mechanics with unique abilities, allowing you to create different strategies to enhance your gameplay, challenge target times, and complete puzzles quickly to earn more rewards! There are also unexpected events and surprises in the game scenes! Most importantly, you can play with family and friends, either cooperatively or competitively, helping or hindering each other\u2014who will be the true puzzle master?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/Customized_Play.gif?t=1735785209\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Puzzle at will. </h2><br>In <strong>Brilliant Jigsaw</strong>, you have complete freedom: puzzle whenever you want, with the ability to save at any time; puzzle whatever image you want by unlocking it with in-game rewards; puzzle however you like, with the freedom to choose and combine various abilities, creating your own unique gameplay style. Additionally, there are multiple themes and color schemes for you to choose from. With this game, you have endless puzzles and limitless possibilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228660/extras/Unlock_Puzzles.gif?t=1735785209\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich and diverse gameplay. </h2><br>Puzzle images range from the budding of life to futuristic communities, from vast landscapes to the cosmos, from treasures to humanity's earliest emotions... With a variety of content, 20+ abilities, and hundreds of combina